;; ============================================================================
;; NOTES FOR AULA F75 KEYBOARD
;; ============================================================================
;; 
;; Layout: 75% (80 keys)
;; - Has dedicated arrow keys (bottom right)
;; - Has F-row keys
;; - No numpad
;; - Compact navigation cluster (Del, PgUp, PgDn, etc.)
;;
;; This config focuses on:
;; 1. Better ergonomics (swap Ctrl/Alt)
;; 2. Vim-style navigation without moving hands
;; 3. Caps Lock → Esc/Nav (most useful remap for programmers)
;;
;; Adjust timings and mappings based on your typing speed and preferences!
